title: Business of Sports: Fantasy Football Week 1 (Podcast)
itunes:title: Business of Sports: Fantasy Football Week 1 (Podcast)
description:
Michael Barr, Rich Trueman, and Damian Sassower bring you the Bloomberg Business of Sports Fantasy Podcast. The trio breaks down the upcoming NFL season and reveal their 2021 draft strategies and sleeper picks.
